parameters: Kyle: "I see. So we couldn't obtain the Holy Grail."
Rinny: "Kyle, what do we do now?"
Kyle: "Without the Holy Grail, our chances of winning are virtually none."

Kyle: "For now, we have no choice but to give up fighting them. We need to think
of another plan... Our only option might be to find Regnus Grahardt himself."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "But in the meantime, who knows how many of the resistance and civilians will
be killed. If only I had more power..."
Kyle: "All we can do now is endure."

Rima: "Luna, there were a boy and a girl who admired you... They followed you
and got lost in the forest. We tried to rescue them but..."
Rima: "Mei and Mao... they were eaten by Hilda."

Wendy: "Luna, I'm sorry. We couldn't protect them. If it were just Hilda, we
might have been able to escape, but with Sylvia, the leader there too... We
simply weren't strong enough to stand against Sylvia..."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Kyle-san, I will go fight them alone if I have to."

Kyle: "Stop. You are an important comrade and a key part of our strength. We
can't afford to lose you now."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I'm sorry. I've already made up my mind."

Rinny: "Kyle is right. Stop this. You don't stand a chance. They are not
opponents you can defeat."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I'm sorry. No one can stop me now. I will go alone."
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] "I'm going too. Those kids were killed for our sake."
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] "Hey hey, with this mood, I've got no choice but to say YES too..."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Kyle, Rinny, thank you for everything up until now. I'm heading to the
imperial capital Jupiterino now."
